{
  "stem": "25912.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, in fact, one of the-- the first raid on Warsaw, the Germans, by mistake, dropped bombs very near where we were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I saw virtually one of the first bombs of the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was scared, but I was also excited.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't know what war meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a new experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, my father, brother, and mother, and brother came to see us on the Sunday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't remember what date it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a lot of talk of what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Father was trying to-- he was an officer in the reserve.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was trying to join the army, but things were rather disorganized at that stage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother, who was a Boy Scout, he wanted to join.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was only 17 at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then-- must have been about the 5th-- we went back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the 7th, the president of the city of Warsaw asked all men to leave the city and declared Warsaw an open city, hoping that that would save it from the ravages of war.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father and my brother left that night, and Mother and myself moved in with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, of course, we didn't hear anything more about them what had happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the bombing of Warsaw started-- open city or no open city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was pretty frightening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the bombs just raining down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my grandparents lived very near the tallest building in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was considered-- called a skyscraper, the Prudential Skyscraper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, by today's standards, it certainly wasn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it had something like 14 stories, or maybe 20.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
